Assembly language translator directories

Merge			-- the merge directory
	atrans		-- the generic part of the assembly language translator
	M68k, I386, M88k, VAX, SPARC, etc
			-- system specific directories
		atr_args.pro	-- argument parsing stuff for one of M68k, I386,
					etc.
		atr_inst.pro	-- instructions for architecture
		Mot, Sun, etc	-- operating system specific (actually assembler
				   specific) directories
			atr_out.pro	--  assembler specific output file
